http.title: AcryliKey Ivory Repair System for Piano Keys
http.html:
AcryliKey® Ivory Repair System
for Piano Keys







AcryliKey is an ivory repair system which uses existing technology in a new way to restore the chipped and disfigured ivory on your customer's Piano keyboard.

Although Ivory piano key repairs with AcryliKey may be done in the customer's piano on site, better results can be achieved in a work shop environment.

If you just wish to clean and disinfect your piano keys we recommend Piano Key Cleaner or Key-Brite both produts will clean, brighten & preserves ivory.






AcryliKey ® Ivory Repair System UK
Tel: 01732 886555 Email: sales@acrylikey.co.uk Fax: 01732 884789
